id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pae1665702621575.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pae1665702621575.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pae1665702621575.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pae1665702621575\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Produce a compiler information message.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"pae1665702621575__topic_d93425e1_d93426e1_d93427e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pae1665702621575__p_d93428e1_d93429e1_d93430e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#info</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Text</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pae1665702621575__section_jgx_rfd_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d549636e66\">Parameters</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pae1665702621575__p_d93434e1_d93435e1_d93436e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Text</var>—compiler message text</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pae1665702621575__section_y5g_tfd_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d549636e78\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pae1665702621575__p_d93440e1_d93441e1_d93442e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#info</span> directive causes the\n            ProcScript compiler to generate an information message. The message\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">Text</var> appears in the Compiler Output tab, and the information\n            message is added to the total for the module being compiled.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pae1665702621575__section_wgg_vfd_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d549636e93\">Example</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pae1665702621575__p_d93443e1_d93444e1_d93445e1\">The following example causes the ProcScript compiler\n            to generate an information message if the compile-time constant\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;MYCONSTANT&gt;</code> has not been defined:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"pae1665702621575__pre_etf_wfd_lwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#ifundefined MYCONSTANT\n #info The constant MYCONSTANT has not been defined.\n#endif\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ycl1665702621117.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>#error</a><p>Produce a compiler error message.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aly1665702621728.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>#warning</a><p>Produce a compiler warning message.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615132\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615132\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "#info Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 29, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Produce a compiler information message. #info Text Parameters Text —compiler message text Description The #info directive causes the ProcScript compiler to generate an information message. The message Text appears in the Compiler Output tab, and the information message is added to the total for the module being compiled. Example The following example causes the ProcScript compiler to generate an information message if the compile-time constant <MYCONSTANT> has not been defined: #ifundefined MYCONSTANT #info The constant MYCONSTANT has not been defined. #endif Copy Related Links #error Produce a compiler error message. #warning Produce a compiler warning message. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}